Title: lvm_vgs: Validate against levels of 0 bytes on free space
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1611603152
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

The rule "Volume Groups (LVM)" and the corresponding check plugin
are not able to deal with levels of 0 imposed on free space.
Please use 100% on used space if this affects you.
